      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, what do you mean by \"mischievous goblins\"? Are you using that as a metaphor for the chemical process or are you talking about something else? Also, you were saying how it gets to the liver—can you finish explaining that part?",
      "source": "evaluator"
